Li Yifan, Sun Zhao, editor of the HSINKING newspaper, vice-chancellor Bai Kui, Zhao Lin

Li Liang died of sudden death from respiratory obstruction and circulatory failure after discharge from the hospital.

Ms. Mei, Li Liang's wife, told the Beijing News that on the day her condition worsened, Li Liang had no symptoms of fever or cough except "dry mouth, a little bloating in the stomach, and weakness in the body. ". Hanyang's Shelter Hospital "after treatment" account, Li Liang twice negative nucleic acid test, meet the discharge criteria. His community also said Li's discharge met the criteria.

Wang Guangfa, a member of the Expert Group of the National Health Commission, told the Beijing News this afternoon that the patient was "false negative" and there was a possibility of "recovering Yang" after discharge from the hospital, but this was mainly due to sampling errors, which were less likely. If there is no obvious new coronary pneumonia disease, should not be too early on its "new pneumonia recurrence" to draw conclusions. He stressed that causes the patient to appear sudden death of respiratory obstruction, respiratory failure factors more, should do further research on this case.

Hanyang Square Cabin Hospital on February 26 issued Li Liang "discharge certificate" , said in the text, after standard treatment, expert group diagnosis confirmed, meet the criteria for discharge of new pneumonia patients, granted discharge. Photo courtesy of the respondents

Four days after discharge from the hospital, "he got sicker. "

Mrs May told the Beijing News today (March 5) that her husband, Li Liang, was treated for new crown pneumonia at the Hanyang International Expo Shelter Hospital in Hanyang. He was discharged after a follow-up check on February 26.

According to a "discharge certificate" issued on February 26 with Hanyang's shelter hospital seal, Li Liang, 36, was admitted to Hanyang's shelter hospital on February 12. After Standard Treatment, the expert group consultation confirmation, conforms to the new coronary pneumonia patient to leave the hospital the standard, authorizes to leave the hospital.

But four days later, Ms May said Li was "getting sicker" .

Ms. May recalled that since March 1, her husband Li Liang can not eat, drink water, feel no sputum in the mouth, stomach distension. On the morning of March 2, Li Liang's temperature was 35.3 degrees Celsius and his pulse was weak. That afternoon, the quarantine hotel doctor called her said, Li Liang mental stress, let it come over counseling, "I arrived in the room, less than 10 minutes, Li Liang will be unconscious. " Subsequently, Ms. Mei emergency call the doctor.

A staff member at the Quarantine Hotel said Li was taken to Wuhan's Fourth Hospital after a 120 emergency call was made.

According to the medical certificate of Resident Death issued by Wuhan No. 4 Hospital, Li Liang's immediate cause of death was "new coronary pneumonia" , and the illness causing the disease was "sudden death due to airway obstruction" and "respiratory circulatory failure" . The time stamp says "March 2,2020. ".

Li Liang "death medical certificate" showed that the direct cause of death for Li Liang "new pneumonia" , cause of the disease specific for "sudden death of Airway Obstruction" , "respiratory circulatory failure" . Photo courtesy of the respondents

No contact with the community while in isolation

Hanyang Shelter Hospital issued a "discharge certificate" special reminder: After discharge, please in the community single isolation 14 days, if feeling unwell, please immediately contact the community responsible person, if necessary to the designated hospital.

In view of the above-mentioned reminder, whether Ms. May's family in Li Liang after the occurrence of symptoms, timely contact the community responsible person? Ms. Mei, responding to the Beijing News, said Li had only been given contact information on the night of March 4 after his death, and had met the community for the first time. "I didn't have a phone number from the community before, " she said

This morning (March 5) , Ms. Mei and her family in Wuhan Qiao Estuary Cloud Crane community relevant responsible person confirmed to the Beijing News Reporter, the community has known Li Liang died in isolation during discharge from the hospital.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Li Liang was placed in an isolated hotel room after being discharged from Hanyang's shelter hospital. Photo courtesy of the respondents

The person in charge said that the community was aware of Li Liang's discharge from the hospital and was under centralized quarantine. "after the discharge of the patient, the street office will make unified arrangements for receiving and transporting the patient, " the person in charge said, the community mainly by volunteers to be quarantined with the delivery of living materials, Li Liang in the hotel during unified isolation, problems can be left to the hotel doctor on duty for help.

The person in charge said that during the quarantine, the family did not take the initiative to contact the community, until the day Li Liang died, the community was informed of his death. On the evening of 4 March, he went to Ms. May's residence to learn about the situation and offered the community's active assistance in case of family difficulties.

The Hsinking news reporter learned from the Vienna Hotel on the third Hanxi road that according to the policy requirement, after Li Liang was discharged from the hospital, he was unified arranged by the street office of his residence to enter the hotel for rehabilitation and isolation.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Li Liang was discharged from the hospital on February 23 before a CT examination. The radiologic diagnosis was "change in both lungs, consistent with viral pneumonia. " . Photo courtesy of the respondents

Three days before discharge, CT was consistent with viral pneumonia

Li had a CT scan on Feb. 23, the day before he left the hospital. The radiologic features of the lesions were: scattered hyperdense Foci in both lungs, mostly with ground glass density, partly with grid-like changes, mostly under the PLEURA, and small nodules in the lower lobe of both lungs, with a maximum diameter of 0.4 cm. The "radiologic diagnosis" was: the lung changes described above, in line with the viral pneumonia.

Li Liang is checked before discharge 3 days, still have certain symptom expression, why can be discharged on February 26? An unidentified first-line medical worker in Hubei Province explained to the Beijing News this afternoon that according to the then-unupdated sixth edition of the COVID-19, the criteria for discharge were "return to normal body temperature for more than 3 days; marked improvement of respiratory symptoms; and marked improvement of acute exudative lesions on lung imaging" .

She analyzed and pointed out that in Li Liang's case, two nucleic acid tests were performed within three days of his discharge from the hospital, which met the requirements and required a "one-day interval, " and his nucleic acid test results were all negative, "In addition, Li Liang's temperature is normal for more than three days, and if the information in these records is accurate, he will meet the discharge criteria. "

According to a "summary of discharge from Hanyang's Shelter Hospital" obtained by a Hsinking newspaper reporter, the "medical treatment process" column describes the treatment process of Li Liang before discharge from Hanyang's shelter hospital.

After Li Liang was admitted to hospital for new pneumonia, he was treated with symptomatic support. His body temperature was normal for more than 3 days, his respiratory symptoms improved obviously, and he was negative for two consecutive nucleic acid tests, the discharge was assessed by a panel of experts.

Hsinking noted that the above "summary" , does not involve the sixth edition of the "diagnosis and treatment of COVID-19 pneumonia" discharge criteria, referred to the "lung imaging showed a significant improvement in acute exudative lesions.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Hanyang Shelter Hospital for Li Liang issued a "diagnosis and treatment process" shows that before discharge, Li Liang temperature normal for more than 3 days, respiratory symptoms significantly improved, two consecutive negative nucleic acid tests... by the expert group assessment, discharged. Photo courtesy of the respondents

Expert: whether recrudesce causes death, unfavorable premature make a conclusion

Li Liang was negative for nucleic acid test two times before discharge from hospital. was there the possibility of "false negative" when he was discharged?

Wang Guangfa, a member of the Expert Group of the National Health Commission and Director of the Department of respiratory and Critical Care Medicine at Peking University First Hospital, told the Beijing News this afternoon (March 5) that the issue of turning negative to positive should be treated with caution and should not be jumped to conclusions. At present, the situation of "Fu Yang" in China may be related to sampling error. He explained that doctors and nurses wearing protective clothing and goggles when in hospital, work is very intense and labor intensity, there may be insufficient sample quality, so there may be "false negative" error.

Wang Guangfa, nucleic acid testing is still a "gold standard" , the method is generally recognized and accepted. Sampling has a lot of attention, such as which parts of the collection, is the collection of nasal swab or throat swab? Is it deep enough? Is the collection sufficient? Might be different. Do you also collect anal swabs or stool samples? If they are collected and tested, the positive rate may be increased. In addition, differences in technology and experience between inpatient and post-discharge testing laboratories should also be considered.

"New Crown" cured why "Fu Yang" ? Or intermittent detox. So far no signs of infection. HSINKING news presents ID: xjbdxw

At the same time, Wang Guangfa stressed that there is another situation in "Fuyang" , that is, the patient has not yet recovered and there is an increase in viral load, "But it's less likely, and with rehabilitation, the amount of detox should be smaller and smaller, not suddenly less and more, " he said, acknowledging that the new coronavirus is unique and can have a two-way course of disease, with a good fever followed by a relapse, this phenomenon is present in some diseases, "but this change is not only accompanied by changes in viral load, but also accompanied by clinical symptoms, such as fever, cough. "

Ms. Mei recalled, Li Liang two times before admission, there is no apparent fever, cough and other symptoms. To this, Wang Guangfa thinks, if be nucleic acid test is positive only, do not accompany symptom, "the likelihood that points to new coronary pneumonia is recrudescent is less. "

For Ms. Mei reflected Li Liang "mouth hair dry, a little bloating, physical weakness, " and other symptoms. Wang Guangfa analysis, Li Liang discharged from the hospital without fever, expectoration performance, in general, unlike new pneumonia re-activity, re-infection of the human performance, the general rule is to appear respiratory symptoms with fever.

Li Liang's death was diagnosed as "sudden death by Airway Obstruction" or "respiratory circulatory failure" . Wang said the hospitalization should be studied to see if there are complications in the treatment of new coronavirus infections, such as secondary heart damage, electrolyte abnormalities and pulmonary embolism, which are also common in hospitalized patients. In addition, whether there are any adverse reactions caused by drugs, or whether there are some underlying diseases that have not been found, "should be well analyzed, not jump to conclusions. From the information reported so far, I personally do not believe that the new pneumonia is not cured. "
